data.description: Here is the home you've been waiting for. This well kept home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an oversized INSULATED 2 car garage and so much room to move around in!  Newer kitchen, roof, windows, paint, carpet and updated bathroom and furnace. Large rooms, wood floors, family room in the basement,  new concrete patio and Concrete alley access. 2nd lot can be used for extra space or a future man cave/she shed. It's all right here!
